summary: I think Liefeld may have plagiarized your Character X, man. '___'
question: I think Liefeld may have plagiarized your Character X, man. '___'
answer:
I’LL SUE THEM. I’LL SUE THEM ALL.

Character X can be found here.

I still cannot fucking believe they made the goddamn cat a “thing”. The fact that Carol had a cat was just a little character quirk, and the fact that the cat was actually dimension hopping, because it came from the House of M reality, was just a stupid continuity bit worthy of an obscure trivia challenge.

But KSD made it a THING. Because she had so little planned for Carol, so few things to say about that character, that she focused more on building the fucking cat’s mythology.

summary: Things I realized in the YJ universe Billy and Jason are almost the same age Jason being 18 and Billy around 17/18... Then I...
caption:
Things I realized in the YJ universe Billy and Jason are almost the same age Jason being 18 and Billy around 17/18… Then I started having connection they both wear Red hoodies/jacket, Blue eyes, black hair….  and they both live in the streets one time…  

So then the idea hits me where Billy Batson somehow ends up in Gotham and made friends with one Jason Todd…. Jason teaching Billy the ropes on how to survive the dangerous City… Billy trying to live on doing the honest and honorable way…. but hey maybe they get picked up by Batman in the future
